Prepare 30g of fresh (or oil-soaked) green Sichuan peppercorns.

0:01:53.025,0:01:55.750
# 最后准备火锅底料35克切散备用
Finally, break down 35g of hot-pot base.

0:01:55.750,0:01:58.450
# 不喜欢红汤的同学可以不加火锅底料
For those who don't like hot soup, you don't have to add the hot-pot base.

0:01:58.450,0:02:00.425
# 也可以改用鸡汁代替
You can also replace it with chicken stock concentrate.

0:02:02.025,0:02:05.100
# 10分钟之后将千层肚捞出沥干水份备用
After 10min, take out the tripe and squeeze out the excess water.

0:02:08.850,0:02:10.325
# 下一步开始制作
Now, let's start cooking.

0:02:10.675,0:02:14.075
# 首先我们在锅中加入适量的清水开大火烧开
First, we add some water into the wok.

0:02:18.350,0:02:20.300
# 中途加入一大勺食用盐（约5克）
We then add a big spoon of salt (5g).

0:02:26.550,0:02:30.425
# 大火烧开之后将所有准备好的垫底辅料下锅焯水2分钟
When the water starts boiling, parboil all of the minor ingredients.

0:02:30.425,0:02:32.750
# 这一步的目的是将辅料煮至断生
This step will soften those ingredients.

0:02:32.750,0:02:35.350
# 辅料下锅之后再加入适量的植物油
Add some vegetable oil into the wok.

0:02:41.850,0:02:44.725
# 焯水2分钟之后捞出放入盆中垫底备用
After blanching for 2min, take out the vegetables and put them in the serving bowl.

0:02:52.600,0:02:55.050
# 锅中再次加入适量的清水烧开
We add water into the wok again until boiling.

0:02:56.800,0:02:58.475
# 中途加入少许的白醋
Add some white vinegar as well.

0:02:58.500,0:03:00.950
# 然后将千层肚下锅烫10秒钟
Put the stomach in for 10 sec.

0:03:00.950,0:03:04.300
# 同学们切记这一步的目的不是将千层肚煮熟
Remember, this step is not to cook the stomach thoroughly，

0:03:04.300,0:03:06.100
# 而是去除一些异味
but to remove some unpleasant smell.

0:03:13.350,0:03:15.475
