Then, add 4g of green chili oil.

0:04:38.550,0:04:41.050
# 30秒钟之后将其捞出放入盆中
After 30 sec, we take everything out and put them into the bowl.

0:04:41.050,0:04:43.075
# 最后再加入适量的原汤
Finally, we add some broth.

